selectForPing

public java.util.ArrayList<Device> selectForPing(PingProtocolType protocol,
                                                 int iteration)
Gets list of devices whose selected ping interface can be utilized this iteration. Does so by selecting devices where (interval % protocol column == 0 or interval == -1) and protocol column > 0

Parameters:
protocol - - protocol type to check for
iteration - - Interval to evaluate against ping protocol column or -1 for all devices with this protocol enabled
Returns:
- ArrayList of Devices
